#: document/templates/admin/document/maintenance.html:4
msgid "Maintenance"
msgstr "Opretholdelse"

#: document/templates/admin/document/maintenance.html:19
msgid ""
"\n"
"            Before and after upgrading Fidus Writer, you should update all the documents\n"
"            of all users to the newest document version. Only do this if you know that\n"
"            no user is currently editing any document!\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Før og efter opgradering af Fidus Writer, bør du opdatere alle dokumenter\n"
"            af alle brugere til den nyeste dokumentversion. Gør kun dette, hvis du ved det\n"
"            ingen bruger redigerer i øjeblikket noget dokument!"

#: document/templates/admin/document/maintenance.html:27
msgid "Update all documents (DANGER!)"
msgstr "Opdater alle dokumenter (FARE!)"

